  "description": "<p><strong>BORING JOB KILLS!!! 😵</strong></p>\n<p><strong>WE are NOT BORING!!! 😜</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You’ll like here because….</p>\n<p>1. You like to be in a hype &amp; dynamic working environment 🦸‍♀️</p>\n<p>2. You want constant support</p>\n<p>3. You are looking for progression (work &amp; personal)🧳</p>\n<p>4. You can work with your friends!👫🏻</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You ok with….</p>\n<p>- Daily meetups with customers from all walks of life</p>\n<p>- Presenting and closing deals</p>\n<p>- IT. Able to keep up with the tech</p>\n<p>- Fast pace environment and able to adapt to change fast</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>You are…</p>\n<p>1. Team Player ⛹️‍♀️</p>\n<p>2. Coachable</p>\n<p>3. Result-driven</p>\n<p>4. Confident communicator</p>\n<p>5. Passionate &amp; Motivated with a Great entrepreneurial mindset</p>\n<p>6. Just ORD/Graduate, don’t know what to do yet</p>\n<p>7. 0️⃣ experience in sales/marketing</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ready! Send your details, we will contact you once you are shortlisted! 💡</strong></p>",
